0:00:00.000,0:00:02.720
Makadii, mukoma?

0:00:02.720,0:00:06.480
Ndiwe wakatengesa mukadzi uyu kana kuti ndiye akakutengesa here?

0:00:06.480,0:00:07.480
Ndini.

0:00:07.480,0:00:11.700
Ndatenda. Ndafara. Uyu muKristu.

0:00:11.700,0:00:13.780
Iwe wakamutengesa sei?

0:00:13.780,0:00:18.560
Izvo zvakaitika munyika yekutanga yandakanga ndichigara apo ndakabuda kunze kwe Nigeria.

0:00:18.560,0:00:21.660
Ndakava ne mwana musikana ne mudzimai wacho.

0:00:21.660,0:00:25.500
Iwe unoziva pakutanga, mwana musikana iyeye, iwe waiedza kumuramba.

0:00:25.500,0:00:26.900
Zvechokwadi.

0:00:26.900,0:00:30.800
Kunyange inzwi rako harina kujeka pamusoro pomwana iyeye.

0:00:30.800,0:00:32.020
hongu.

0:00:32.020,0:00:33.620
Mwana wacho ari kugara naye?

0:00:33.620,0:00:34.400
Hongu changamire.

0:00:34.400,0:00:37.760
Zvakaitika ndezvekuti, pandakanga ndiri munyika iyoyo yekutanga,

0:00:37.760,0:00:40.600
Ndakabva munyika iyoyo ndokuenda kunzvimbo imwe.

0:00:40.600,0:00:43.180
Pandakasvika ikoko, ndakasangana nemumwe munhu.

0:00:43.180,0:00:47.360
Ndicho chikonzero ndakanga ndisingakwanisi kumuroora.

0:00:47.360,0:00:49.340
Aripi mwana iye zvino? Aripi mukadzi wacho?

0:00:49.340,0:00:50.820
Ari ku Libreville, Gabon.

0:00:50.820,0:00:54.020
Ndirini apo wakanzwa kubva kumwana naamai vake?

0:00:54.020,0:00:56.440
Ndakanzwa kubva kwavari mwedzi miviri yapfuura.

0:00:56.440,0:00:57.080
Mwedzi miviri yapfuura?

0:00:57.080,0:00:57.900
Hongu.

0:00:57.900,0:01:01.000
Akakuudzei nokuti pane chimwe chinhu chaairamba achikuudza?

0:01:01.000,0:01:02.800
Ndicho chikonzero chikuru chandakudana iwe.

0:01:02.800,0:01:07.060
Akandiudza kuti aida kutanga bhizinesi,

0:01:07.060,0:01:08.700
kuti ini ndinofanira kumutangira bhizinesi,

0:01:08.700,0:01:10.320
Saka akati aida rubatsiro rwako.

0:01:10.320,0:01:11.100
Hongu.

0:01:11.100,0:01:16.800
Akati anoda rubatsiro rwako. Mupe mari uye umufonere kuti akunyengeterere.

0:01:16.800,0:01:18.980
Iye mukadzi akatendeka.

0:01:18.980,0:01:23.500
Panguva yawakasangana naye, mushure mokunge wapinda muhupenyu hwake, iwe wakamuvhiringidza.

0:01:23.500,0:01:25.260
Iye haachaziva zvekuita zvakare.

0:01:25.260,0:01:27.580
Haana kunyange neimba yakagadzikana.

0:01:27.580,0:01:28.460
Zvechokwadi.

0:01:28.460,0:01:31.680
Dai zvaikwanisika, aizoda kuroorwa newe zvakare nokuti haakwanisi kuroorwa ne umwe munhu.

0:01:31.680,0:01:35.380
Akandiudza kuti ndini 'murume woupenyu hwake'.

0:01:35.380,0:01:39.680
Iwe unomuda. Mamiriro ezvinhu ndiwo akakuchinja iwe ikoko.

0:01:39.680,0:01:43.220
Iwe wakanga uchitsvaga nzira yekuve ne budiriro.

0:01:43.220,0:01:47.740
Zvechokwadi, mwoyo wako uriku mukadzi uyu asi iwe haugoni kuve nevaviri zvakare.

0:01:47.740,0:01:50.620
Iwe unofanirwa kugara neuyu uye ukanganwe nezve iyeye.

0:01:50.620,0:01:54.740
Panguva ino iye zvino haugoni kumuroora asi iwe unofanira kumuita kuti afare.

0:01:54.740,0:01:55.540
Ndinokutendai, changamire.

0:01:55.540,0:01:57.960
Pasina kununurwa, haagoni kukukanganwa.

0:01:57.960,0:02:00.120
Pasina dzikinuro, haazombororwi zvachose.

0:02:00.120,0:02:02.860
Haana rudo kune ani zvake.

0:02:02.860,0:02:05.680
Mushure memari yauri kuzomupa.

0:02:05.680,0:02:08.860
mupe iye nemwanasikana wake mari yetikiti kuti auye kumunamato.

0:02:08.860,0:02:14.700
Mushure memunyengetero, zvino anogona kuita rudo rwekuroorwa ne umwe munhu.

0:02:14.700,0:02:17.480
Anoramba ari amai vemwana wako.

0:02:17.480,0:02:21.100
Iwe unogona kumubatsira mangwana asi iye achakusiya uye iwe uchamusiya.

0:02:21.100,0:02:22.480
Saka ndizvo zvazviri. Ndatenda.

0:02:22.480,0:02:28.780
Nguva Ye Huporofita

0:02:28.780,0:02:30.560
Muzita ra Jesu!

0:02:30.560,0:02:33.320
Kununurwa Mu Zita ra Jesu

0:02:33.320,0:02:37.820
Ndinokutendai, Ishe. Muzita raJesu Kristu.

0:02:37.820,0:02:43.100
Kutevera huporofita hwemunhu wa Mwari, mu Porofita T.B. Joshua, uye achitsigirwa naye,

0:02:43.100,0:02:47.520
murume wacho akatumira ku mwanasikana wake na amai vake vaakanga aramba.

0:02:47.520,0:02:54.540
Vakasanganazve kamwe zvakare kekutanga mushure memakore 12 akareba pa SCOAN.

0:02:54.540,0:02:57.940
Ngationei kusangana kwavo.

0:02:57.940,0:03:00.800
Urikuona simba reuporofita here?

0:03:00.800,0:03:07.180
Uyu musikana akanaka angadai akarasikirwa pakupedzisira, saizvozvo, dai pasina huporofita.

0:03:07.180,0:03:11.920
Hwaiva huporofita ihwohwo hwakaita kuti abvume kuti ndiye baba vacho.

0:03:11.920,0:03:14.300
Zita rangu ndi Elijah Chikwendu.

0:03:14.300,0:03:18.840
Ndiri wemu Nigeria asi ndiri kugara ku DRC.

0:03:18.840,0:03:30.140
Chakaitika ndechokuti ndaive nematambudziko akawanda muupenyu hwangu.

0:03:30.140,0:03:35.720
Ndakanga ndichitsvaga nzira yekubuda nayo mu matambudziko.

0:03:35.720,0:03:40.720
Ndakauya pa SCOAN gore rapera.

0:03:40.720,0:03:49.800
Munhu wa Mwari akaporofita kwandiri kuti pane mukadzi wandakanga ndagumbura.

0:03:49.800,0:03:55.500
Ndakabvuma nokuti ndaiziva kuti munhu wa Mwari haandizive.

0:03:55.500,0:04:04.400
Akaporofita chaizvoizvo zvakanga zvaitika muupenyu hwangu hwekare.

0:04:04.400,0:04:11.760
Akandiudza kuti ndiende ndinouya ne musikana wacho kuNigeria kuzonunurwa

0:04:11.760,0:04:18.500
kuitira kuti asununguke uye ave noupenyu hutsva

0:04:18.500,0:04:24.120
nokuti sekuona kwamuri kuita ikozvino, ndakaroora nevana vana.

0:04:24.120,0:04:30.460
Mwanasikana wangu pano - Handina kumuona kwemakore 12 apfuura izvozvi.

0:04:30.460,0:04:35.540
Sezvamuri kumuona iye pano, iyi ndiyo nguva yangu yokutangawo kumuona.

0:04:35.540,0:04:43.780
Munhu wa Mwari, ndapota, ndinoda rubatsiro rwenyu.

0:04:43.780,0:04:48.220
Izvi ndizvo zvinodzivisa vazhinji venyu.

0:04:48.220,0:04:51.140
Ati iye ari kumuona kekutanga.

0:04:51.140,0:04:55.440
Asi iwe uri kutsvaga budiriro, chikomborero.

0:04:55.440,0:04:57.680
Varoyi ne vauki ndivo honzeri.

0:04:57.680,0:05:02.520
Asi isu hatizivi izvo zvatakakonzeresa tenga pachedu.

0:05:02.520,0:05:08.240
99% yematambudziko edu anokonzerwa nesu pachedu.

0:05:08.240,0:05:14.720
Saka zvino, kana izvi zvagadziriswa, iwe unofanira kuchengeta mwana, kubhadhara mari yechikoro,

0:05:14.720,0:05:18.460
chero izvo mukadzi uyu angave akabhadhara kwemakore 12 apfuura.

0:05:18.460,0:05:24.180
Iwe unofanirwa kugara pasi nekukurukurirana - kuyananisa, kupa mari

0:05:24.180,0:05:28.340
uye utore mutoro wemwanasikana wako sababa.

0:05:28.340,0:05:33.920
Uye chero chipi zvacho chaunoda kuti upe mukadzi uyu, mupe ichocho uye ugare uchiita sababa.

0:05:33.920,0:05:38.240
Uye ramangwana rakajeka.

0:05:38.240,0:05:40.780
Chidziviso chabviswa.

0:05:40.780,0:05:46.160
Vazhinji venyu hamuzivi kuti ichi ndicho chinokonzero  matambudziko enyu.

0:05:46.160,0:05:50.960
Ndicho chikonzero, zvisinei nemunyengetero waunopa, munyengetero wako haugone kupindurwa.

0:05:50.960,0:05:54.700
Nokuti chimwe chinhu chiripo chinoda kubviswa - gomo.

0:05:54.700,0:05:58.160
Zvisinei nekutsanya - kana iwe ukatsanya kwemazuva makumi mana neusiku makumi mana;

0:05:58.160,0:06:03.880
uye kunamata ne kuenda kugomo, hapana chichaitika.

0:06:03.880,0:06:09.060
Kunze kwekunge wasangana nomunhu wa Mwari uyo achakuudza, "Iri ndiro gomo raunofanira kubvisa".

0:06:09.060,0:06:13.160
Kana iwe ukabvisa gomo iri uchiti "Jesu!", Jesu achakunzwa.

0:06:13.160,0:06:16.740
Asi kana iwe usingabvisi gomo iroro uye iwe unoramba uchidanidzira "Jesu!" -

0:06:16.740,0:06:20.980
chimwe chinhu chirikukudzivirira - chiri pakati pako na Jesu.

0:06:20.980,0:06:23.100
Dzimwe nguva unoti, "Iwe unonamata, unotsanya".

0:06:23.100,0:06:25.240
Vazhinji venyu munoti, "Ndave mu Kristu ikozvino".

0:06:25.240,0:06:27.740
Zvino iwe unotanga kuva akatendeka, mutsa.

0:06:27.740,0:06:29.840
Kana iwe waiva chidhakwa, iwe unorega kunwa.

0:06:29.840,0:06:31.760
Kana iwe waiva murevi wenhema, iwe unorega kureva nhema.

0:06:31.760,0:06:34.000
Kana waive mbavha, iwe unorega kuba.

0:06:34.000,0:06:35.980
Iwe unotanga kurarama hupenyu hwakanaka

0:06:35.980,0:06:37.780
Vanhu vanotanga kuti, "Iye ave muKristu iye zvino".

0:06:37.780,0:06:40.500
Asi zvakadaro, hupenyu hwacho hauna kuchinja.

0:06:40.500,0:06:45.520
Vanhu vanoti, "Asi murume uyu akarega kuenda kumabhawa, iye zvino ari kuenda kuchechi.

0:06:45.520,0:06:49.900
Iye atori mukuru muchechi, anotsanya, iye mubatsiri,

0:06:49.900,0:06:54.080
iye muerudha, iye muiti wa zvose, anogara ari pamba, ari kuparidza vhangeri,

0:06:54.080,0:06:56.940
asi hupenyu hwake hauna kuchinja. Sei?"

0:06:56.940,0:06:59.380
Pane chipingamupinyi.

0:06:59.380,0:07:03.440
Zvose izvozvo zvemutsa, zvakanaka - Mwari haasi kuzvinzwa.

0:07:03.440,0:07:07.340
Kusvikira chipingamupinyi ichocho chabviswa.

0:07:07.340,0:07:13.660
Gomo Iwe uchabva, o gomo

0:07:13.660,0:07:20.800
Iwe uchabva sekutaura kwandirikuita ikozvino muzita ra Jesu

0:07:20.800,0:07:26.960
Gomo Iwe uchabva

0:07:26.960,0:07:30.000
Icho chidzidzo. Hazvisi izvo zvakaitika kumurume uyu zvinokosha zvino

0:07:30.000,0:07:33.940
asi chidzidzo chamuchadzidza nhasi kubva munyaya iyi.

0:07:33.940,0:07:40.660
Chidzidzo chamunodzidza nhasi chakanyanya kukosha kudarika izvo murume uyu ari kutaura.

0:07:40.660,0:07:47.380
Munhu wa Mwari, uporofita hwamakapa kwandiri ndohwechokwadi.

0:07:47.380,0:07:50.140
Chakaitika ndechokuti mushure mehuporofita,

0:07:50.140,0:07:54.040
pane zvimwe zvinhu zvandakayeuka zvandakaita

0:07:54.040,0:08:00.700
uye uporofita husati hwaitika, zvinhu zvose izvi zvakanga zvisiri mupfungwa dzangu.

0:08:00.700,0:08:06.780
Mushure mohuporofita, ndakarangarira kuti paakabereka mwana wangu,

0:08:06.780,0:08:12.320
pane chimwe chinhu chandakaenda kumhuri yavo kunoita.

0:08:12.320,0:08:16.340
Kwaiva kutaura kumhuri, pasina kuziva

0:08:16.340,0:08:23.380
kuti zvichava nemigumisiro kwaari kana ini pachangu munguva ichateera.

0:08:23.380,0:08:29.580
Paiva pashure pehuporofita apo ndakaziva kuti munzvimbo yavo,

0:08:29.580,0:08:36.760
zvaireva kuti aizondimirira.

0:08:36.760,0:08:43.980
Zvino, sezvazviri, ini ndakaroora; iye haana kuroorwa zvakare.

0:08:43.980,0:08:47.980
Munhu wa Mwari, ndapota, sezvo ikozvino ndakaroora,

0:08:47.980,0:08:50.940
Ndinoda kuti mundibatsire kuputsa sungano

0:08:50.940,0:08:55.640
kuitira kuti mukadzi uyu asunungurwe uye aroorwe zvakare.

0:08:55.640,0:08:56.980
Zvakanaka

0:08:56.980,0:08:59.800
Mukadzi uyu anofanira kusunungurwa.

0:08:59.800,0:09:04.200
Mudzimai uyu anoda kudzikinurwa kuitira kuti abvise pfungwa dzake pamurume uyu.

0:09:04.200,0:09:11.240
Nemhaka yemakore 15 apfuura, iye achiri kuvimba kuti murume uyu aiva murume wake.

0:09:11.240,0:09:15.880
Zvakadaro, hapana munhu akafanana nemurume uyu kwaari.

0:09:15.880,0:09:16.840
Hapana!

0:09:16.840,0:09:19.180
Kana iye akangoona chero munhu - murume akanaka -

0:09:19.180,0:09:23.080
iye anongoti, "Haana kufuta semurume uyu".

0:09:23.080,0:09:26.600
Kana achiona umwe - "Haana kupfupika sezvakaita murume uyu."

0:09:26.600,0:09:35.420
Kana akaona umwe - "Haagoni kusvoda se murume uyu."

0:09:35.420,0:09:37.200
Kune dambudziko!

0:09:37.200,0:09:44.600
Sungano iyoyo inofanira kuputswa kuitira kuti mukadzi iyeye asunungurwe.

0:09:44.600,0:09:47.680
Zvakanaka, uyu mwanasikana wako muduku?

0:09:47.680,0:09:49.320
Hongu.

0:09:49.320,0:09:54.220
Saka isu tichazotaura, izvo mukadzi uyu akapedzera pa musikana uyu.

0:09:54.220,0:09:57.320
Yakawanda sei? - Ndichagara pamusangano wacho

0:09:57.320,0:10:01.060
uye iwe uchachengeta mwanasikana uyu.

0:10:01.060,0:10:03.240
Iwe uchaita kuti mudzimai uyu agadzikike -

0:10:03.240,0:10:08.340
chero chipi zvacho chaunogona kumupa kuti atange hupenyu hwake mushure mekununurwa kuitira kuti vagoenda.

0:10:08.340,0:10:11.880
Kuvandudzwa kwekasikana aka kuchava mutoro wako.

0:10:11.880,0:10:27.180
Chero chaangadai akaparadza munguva yapfuura kubvira apo musikana uyu aiva mucheche, tinofanira kuzvidzorera.

0:10:27.180,0:10:31.380
Ndiyo vandudzo, kwete dzikinuro chete.

0:10:31.380,0:10:33.760
Zvichaenderana ne vandudzo.

0:10:33.760,0:10:39.360
Tinochengeta musikana uyu, uye achauya kuzokushanyira nekukutora sababa vake.

0:10:39.360,0:10:41.560
Uye newewo uchaenda kumba kwake kunomukwazisa.

0:10:41.560,0:10:45.520
Iwe unofanirwa kuuudza mudzimai wako kumba. Ndinoda kuona iyeye zvakare.

0:10:45.520,0:10:51.540
Kuita kuti azive kuti mukadzi uyu inhengo yemhuri iyi.

0:10:51.540,0:10:54.060
Haisi chinhu chaunoita muchivande.

0:10:54.060,0:10:59.100
Nokuti kana uchiita izvi muchivande, hazvizove nechiremerera.

0:10:59.100,0:11:02.060
Iwe unofanira kumurega azive; uye ini ndichamurega azive.

0:11:02.060,0:11:07.780
Hazvizovhiringidza imba yako asi ziva kuti, iye inhengo ye mhuri iyi.

0:11:07.780,0:11:09.960
Ndokutendai zvikuru.

0:11:09.960,0:11:13.780
Munhu wa Mwari, ndapota, ndibatsirei kuti ndivakumbire kuti vandikanganwire - kunyange mwanasikana wangu.

0:11:13.780,0:11:19.540
Kubvira Mugovera, aisagona kuuya pedyo neni; iye aingochema.

0:11:19.540,0:11:22.120
Nokuti haakuzive.

0:11:22.120,0:11:26.180
Akanga ane mufananidzo wako paakanga achiri muduku.

0:11:26.180,0:11:34.680
Fungidzira kuti waitarisika sei makore gumi ne maviri apfuura uye kuti uri kutarisika sei ikozvino.

0:11:34.680,0:11:38.620
Mushure me svondo tichagadzirisa zvinhu zvose; zvose zvichava zvakanaka.

0:11:38.620,0:11:42.180
Makadii? Munobva kupi?

0:11:42.180,0:11:44.480
Isu tinobva ku Gabon.

0:11:44.480,0:11:45.960
Zvakanaka

0:11:45.960,0:11:47.700
Wagamuchirwa!

0:11:47.700,0:11:50.260
Tsanangurai zvangu ini, ndapota.

0:12:30.780,0:12:35.760
Regai amai nemwanasikana vazive kuti Mwari akazvibata zvese.

0:12:35.760,0:12:38.480
Mushure me svondo, ndinoda kusangana navo.

0:12:38.480,0:12:43.020
Iye achagamuchira dzikinuro yakakwana kuitira kuti aone kukosha kwake kwechokwadi

0:12:43.020,0:12:45.520
uye kuti anofambira mberi sei.

0:12:45.520,0:12:52.120
Ndinoda kuti iye aregerere murume uyu pano nokuti Mwari akanganwira murume uyu.

0:12:52.120,0:12:56.560
Saka, anofanira kuregerera murume uyu uye achaita chinhu chakanaka.

0:13:16.380,0:13:19.200
Regai nditaure nekasikana kadiki.

0:13:19.200,0:13:30.000
Sei akanga achitiza kubva kuna baba vake?

0:13:30.000,0:13:34.220
Vakandisiya.

0:13:34.220,0:13:37.040
Usamubvunze umwe mubvunzo, ndapota.

0:13:37.040,0:13:38.240
Huya.

0:13:45.200,0:13:49.960
Usanetseka, nhaika? Ndichamuona pakarepo mushure me svondo.

0:13:49.960,0:13:54.980
Uye iye achafara zvikuru nokuti Mwari ari mazviri.

0:13:54.980,0:13:59.280
Mwari ari mazviri.

0:13:59.280,0:14:00.640
Urikuona here?

0:14:00.640,0:14:03.900
Haana shoko rakakodzera kune izvozvo.

0:14:03.900,0:14:07.280
Shoko rinobaya kwazvo: Vakandisiya!

0:14:07.280,0:14:12.240
Kwete kuedza kuzvitsanangura - Vakandisiya!

0:14:12.240,0:14:15.780
Nenzira yekukurumidza. Urikuona here pfini!

0:14:15.780,0:14:19.280
Saka usanetseka. Ndinoda kukuona.

0:14:19.280,0:14:24.640
Ane makore mangani iye zvino?

0:14:24.640,0:14:27.800
Ndine makore 14.

0:14:27.800,0:14:29.760
Zvinoreva kuti, aiva nemakore maviri.

0:14:29.760,0:14:34.900
Hapana nzira iyo aigona kuziva murume uyu.

0:14:34.900,0:14:36.020
Ndatenda.

0:14:36.020,0:14:38.800
